207
00:12:20,540 --> 00:12:21,540
Mr. Sima!

208
00:12:24,780 --> 00:12:25,940
You idiot!

209
00:12:26,340 --> 00:12:27,700
Do you know the consequence of

210
00:12:27,700 --> 00:12:29,420
