218
00:12:55,260 --> 00:12:56,220
Let him go.

219
00:12:59,740 --> 00:13:00,500
What?

220
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:05,380
Just let him go.

221
00:13:10,060 --> 00:13:11,260
Just let him go?

222
00:13:12,060 --> 00:13:13,740
How dares he break down the Emperor’s gift!

223
00:13:13,740 --> 00:13:15,460
He should be given a life sentence.

224
00:13:17,220 --> 00:13:19,060
