and easy to disappear.

234
00:13:42,340 --> 00:13:45,020
Mistakes of the servant by accident
could also be forgiven.

235
00:13:51,220 --> 00:13:52,060
In my opinion,

236
00:13:52,940 --> 00:13:55,420
