259
00:14:41,460 --> 00:14:42,140
Therefore…

260
00:14:49,420 --> 00:14:50,660
I got to investigate this immediately.

261
00:14:50,900 --> 00:14:51,620
No need to do so.

262
00:14:55,940 --> 00:14:57,420
Fortunately, it’s Sima Guang!

263
00:14:58,060 --> 00:14:59,740
He’s known to be a nice person.

264
00:15:00,940 --> 00:15:03,020
He used to break a big jar to save people
when he was a child.

265
00:15:06,020 --> 00:15:06,820
Wait a minute!

266
00:15:08,660 --> 00:15:09,820
You said

267
00:15:10,340 --> 00:15:12,020
= Zhang Chengzhao =
it was not long before that

268
00:15:12,020 --> 00:15:12,900
Mr. Sima opened the box,

269
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:14,580
Officer Ren burst in with his men?

270
00:15:16,220 --> 00:15:18,500
Probably in less than 5 minutes.

271
00:15:18,670 --> 00:15:19,130
What?

272
00:15:20,340 --> 00:15:22,180
It’s not a coincidence!

273
00:15:23,460 --> 00:15:24,900
You helped a eunuch

274
00:15:24,900 --> 00:15:26,100
