277
00:15:29,860 --> 00:15:30,980
Not long before you opened it

278
00:15:31,380 --> 00:15:33,220
Ren Shouzhong, the most strict and poker-faced man,

279
00:15:33,220 --> 00:15:34,620
in the Ministry of Internal Service

280
00:15:34,780 --> 00:15:35,820
burst in with his men.

281
00:15:37,660 --> 00:15:39,340
It’s definitely a trap.

282
00:15:44,540 --> 00:15:45,420
Have you ever

283
00:15:45,740 --> 00:15:47,300
offended someone recently?

284
00:15:51,340 --> 00:15:52,620
When it comes to offense,

285
00:15:53,540 --> 00:15:55,020
only Lady Zhang would count.

286
00:15:55,180 --> 00:15:56,180
Zhang, Zhang?

287
00:15:58,220 --> 00:15:59,180
What’s going on?

288
00:16:07,060 --> 00:16:08,180
Chuyue passed away.

289
00:16:09,820 --> 00:16:13,300
You felt upset. So do I.

290
00:16:17,300 --> 00:16:18,660
However, in this real world,

291
00:16:18,660 --> 00:16:20,660
there’s always something imperfect,

292
00:16:21,700 --> 00:16:24,220
something making us disappointed, sad,

293
00:16:25,180 --> 00:16:26,860
and even resented.

294
00:16:28,020 --> 00:16:29,620
Even the heaven can do nothing about it.

295
00:16:32,580 --> 00:16:34,340
I know how grieved you are

296
00:16:34,900 --> 00:16:36,580
for being helpless to protect the closest one.

297
00:16:36,780 --> 00:16:37,940
I know it’s unacceptable.

298
00:16:39,420 --> 00:16:41,260
Your Majesty, Chuyue was…

299
00:16:41,260 --> 00:16:42,100
Bihan.

300
00:16:43,580 --> 00:16:45,140
Chuyue was congenitally deficient.

301
00:16:46,340 --> 00:16:48,500
We’ve done our best to hold her life.

302
00:16:52,820 --> 00:16:54,420
I don’t want you to vent this anger on others

303
00:16:56,860 --> 00:16:58,700
and hurt innocent people.

304
00:17:01,420 --> 00:17:03,180
Gather up everyone in the Pavilion of Luan.

305
00:17:03,780 --> 00:17:04,900
I have something to say.

306
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:06,860
Yes, Your Majesty.

307
00:17:13,620 --> 00:17:14,980
Go to sleep quickly.

308
00:17:15,460 --> 00:17:16,900
If you don’t sleep well at night,

309
00:17:16,980 --> 00:17:19,580
you’d fall asleep at class tomorrow,

310
00:17:19,820 --> 00:17:22,060
and turn out to be waked up by your teacher
in the unconscious state.

311
00:17:22,340 --> 00:17:25,060
You may mis-recite the
stepping-on-wood-chair as flourished plants

312
00:17:25,300 --> 00:17:27,580
and again translate it like
the ancient people would step on the wood chair

313
00:17:27,580 --> 00:17:29,940
to steal prunes as well.

314
00:17:31,140 --> 00:17:32,460
Mother,

315
00:17:32,460 --> 00:17:35,060
You repeated this like a hundred times.

316
00:17:37,540 --> 00:17:39,220
OK I’ll tell another story.

317
00:17:39,860 --> 00:17:40,820
Come on, Mother.

318
00:17:41,940 --> 00:17:42,700
Close your eyes now.

319
00:17:44,540 --> 00:17:45,500
Mother,

320
00:17:45,620 --> 00:17:47,900
Which book tells the story of Consort Ban?

321
00:17:47,900 --> 00:17:49,260
I want to read about that.

322
00:17:49,940 --> 00:17:51,540
A little girl
who only knows to step on wood chair to

323
00:17:51,540 --> 00:17:52,980
stole prunes

324
00:17:53,340 --> 00:17:54,820
wouldn’t know about this

325
00:17:54,860 --> 00:17:55,860
until she gets married.

326
00:17:57,260 --> 00:17:58,460
Mother,

327
00:18:00,980 --> 00:18:01,780
OK

328
00:18:02,500 --> 00:18:04,180
Actually I don’t know it either.

329
00:18:05,420 --> 00:18:07,420
Go ask the Empress tomorrow.

330
00:18:10,100 --> 00:18:10,900
Huirou,

331
00:18:12,260 --> 00:18:13,060
don’t tell anyone about this

332
00:18:13,660 --> 00:18:15,780
anymore.

333
00:18:16,260 --> 00:18:17,060
OK.

334
00:18:19,700 --> 00:18:21,180
Treating you unjustly

335
00:18:21,980 --> 00:18:23,220
is Lady Zhang’s fault.

336
00:18:24,100 --> 00:18:27,780
But ever since Chuyue was sick and later died,

337
00:18:28,460 --> 00:18:29,820
she’s the one who had her heart broken.

338
00:18:31,300 --> 00:18:32,620
So let’s forgive her,

339
00:18:33,060 --> 00:18:33,860
shall we?

340
00:18:35,820 --> 00:18:38,580
Like nothing happened.

341
00:18:40,340 --> 00:18:41,460
She doesn’t like you.

342
00:18:41,900 --> 00:18:43,140
Neither do you.

343
00:18:44,180 --> 00:18:46,700
So just keep distance with her.

344
00:18:47,740 --> 00:18:48,740
When you meet her ,

345
00:18:49,380 --> 00:18:51,380
you should still treat her with due respect.

346
00:18:51,660 --> 00:18:52,540
OK.

347
00:18:53,540 --> 00:18:54,460
Mother,

348
00:18:54,540 --> 00:18:56,820
Is Chuyue really being cursed

349
00:18:56,820 --> 00:18:58,500
to get sick?

350
00:18:58,740 --> 00:19:00,180
Who is the bad guy?

351
00:19:01,220 --> 00:19:01,940
Taotao,

352
00:19:02,260 --> 00:19:03,500
I said,

353
00:19:04,660 --> 00:19:06,820
don’t talk about this anymore.

354
00:19:08,980 --> 00:19:11,100
That’s all I want to say.

355
00:19:12,700 --> 00:19:15,700
From now on, take good care of Madam Zhang.

356
00:19:17,060 --> 00:19:18,780
If any of you do something wrong,

357
00:19:19,060 --> 00:19:21,020
but not on purpose,
I wouldn’t blame on you.

358
00:19:21,860 --> 00:19:23,260
if you say something you shouldn’t

359
00:19:23,820 --> 00:19:25,380
and bother her

360
00:19:25,540 --> 00:19:27,180
to generate fabricated confusion

361
00:19:27,940 --> 00:19:29,220
then you'd be given a capital crime.

362
00:19:39,220 --> 00:19:40,020
I have thought to arrange Liang Huaiji,

363
00:19:40,020 --> 00:19:41,580
one of my favorite eunuchs,

364
00:19:41,780 --> 00:19:43,380
to serve you.

365
00:19:43,900 --> 00:19:46,900
but, who knows?

366
00:19:48,260 --> 00:19:49,180
I thought

367
00:19:50,260 --> 00:19:51,620
now that he could calm down

368
00:19:51,620 --> 00:19:53,100
to work with the Imperial Academy,

369
00:19:54,260 --> 00:19:56,220
It’s good for him

370
00:19:56,220 --> 00:19:57,180
to read and copy those books for his whole life.

371
00:19:57,900 --> 00:20:02,180
Who can expect that he was framed today?

372
00:20:04,820 --> 00:20:05,940
To prevent something like this,

373
00:20:06,020 --> 00:20:07,100
from happening again,

374
00:20:07,820 --> 00:20:09,460
I have to assign him to the Hall
of Happiness and Tranquility to

375
00:20:09,780 --> 00:20:12,180
wait upon me.

376
00:20:21,540 --> 00:20:22,260
It’s too late.

377
00:20:23,980 --> 00:20:25,940
Take Madam Zhang to bed.

378
00:20:26,740 --> 00:20:28,660
if this happens again,

379
00:20:29,140 --> 00:20:32,140
I’ll get the Imperial Security Agency involved

380
00:20:32,340 --> 00:20:33,460
to investigate this thoroughly.

381
00:20:35,460 --> 00:20:36,220
Rise.

382
00:21:06,460 --> 00:21:07,420
Huaiji, Huaiji,

383
00:21:07,460 --> 00:21:08,380
What’s up?

384
00:21:09,700 --> 00:21:10,980
that way, that way, go to that way.

385
00:21:11,100 --> 00:21:11,940
Take 19 steps.

386
00:21:12,060 --> 00:21:12,860
For what?

387
00:21:13,340 --> 00:21:14,740
I thought it through last night.

388
00:21:14,940 --> 00:21:16,460
You offended a badass.

389
00:21:16,460 --> 00:21:17,460
Such a disaster,

390
00:21:17,460 --> 00:21:18,620
if you don’t work through this,

391
00:21:18,700 --> 00:21:20,540
it may become a doom.

392
00:21:21,260 --> 00:21:22,420
I used to learn

393
00:21:22,420 --> 00:21:23,500
a way to avert disaster.

394
00:21:33,060 --> 00:21:33,940
Liang Huaiji,

395
00:21:35,620 --> 00:21:37,380
Go get your belongings

396
00:21:38,060 --> 00:21:38,940
and come with me.

397
00:21:43,220 --> 00:21:45,860
Your Majesty, I bring Liang Huaiji here.

398
00:21:46,900 --> 00:21:48,460
Ok. Take him in.

399
00:21:53,900 --> 00:21:55,980
My respect to Your Majesty.

400
00:21:57,180 --> 00:21:58,100
Officer Ren told me

401
00:21:58,540 --> 00:22:00,340
about what happened yesterday.

402
00:22:00,740 --> 00:22:02,100
Do you want to explain

403
00:22:02,380 --> 00:22:03,660
why you broke the Emperor’s gift?

404
00:22:03,780 --> 00:22:04,820
Is there something you want to tell me?

405
00:22:07,340 --> 00:22:09,420
I’m guilty. Please punish me, Your Majesty.

406
00:22:11,540 --> 00:22:13,460
Ok, come with me.

407
00:22:20,340 --> 00:22:21,180
Father!

408
00:22:38,900 --> 00:22:40,140
It’s been 2 months

409
00:22:40,350 --> 00:22:41,400
since you’ve learned the Book of Rites.

410
00:22:42,180 --> 00:22:44,260
= Shi Jie, courtesy name Shoudao =
Today His Majesty comes here

411
00:22:45,100 --> 00:22:46,060
with a eunuch

412
00:22:46,140 --> 00:22:48,220
= Zhao Zongshi =
who made a mistake by accident.

413
00:22:48,580 --> 00:22:50,740
By hearing what he did,

414
00:22:51,620 --> 00:22:52,540
go make a judge by yourself

415
00:22:53,180 --> 00:22:55,380
from the aspect of

416
00:22:55,740 --> 00:22:56,780
rites or feelings.

417
00:22:57,380 --> 00:23:00,620
Show me what you’ve learned.

418
00:23:03,220 --> 00:23:04,940
Alright, don’t be mad.

419
00:23:06,220 --> 00:23:08,020
His Majesty came yesterday

420
00:23:08,300 --> 00:23:09,820
and gathered all the servants
of the pavilion together.

421
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:11,860
He kept staring at me

422
00:23:12,020 --> 00:23:13,860
when he was speaking,

423
00:23:15,180 --> 00:23:16,100
He must have thought that

424
00:23:16,940 --> 00:23:17,740
it was me who

425
00:23:18,300 --> 00:23:20,180
did it without letting you know

426
00:23:20,660 --> 00:23:22,820
or I told you to do so.

427
00:23:23,460 --> 00:23:24,940
He must have not blamed

428
00:23:25,060 --> 00:23:26,340
on you.

429
00:23:30,220 --> 00:23:31,980
It was me who worried
that you’d prevent me from doing this,

430
00:23:32,820 --> 00:23:34,860
so I ask the others to do that.

431
00:23:35,460 --> 00:23:36,580
It’s none of your business.

432
00:23:38,780 --> 00:23:40,300
I’m responsible for what I did.

433
00:23:41,140 --> 00:23:42,860
I’m going to tell the truth to His Majesty.

434
00:23:43,940 --> 00:23:45,340
Don’t be such a baby.

435
00:23:47,100 --> 00:23:49,780
I’m not stopping you to revenge for Chuyue.

436
00:23:50,900 --> 00:23:52,900
Instead, I want you to do so,

437
00:23:53,180 --> 00:23:55,260
but thoroughly

438
00:23:55,420 --> 00:23:57,300
keep our hands clean
and clear all the obstacles for good.

439
00:23:58,500 --> 00:24:00,540
I am now unable to know

440
00:24:00,780 --> 00:24:01,700
why and when

441
00:24:01,900 --> 00:24:02,860
the glass cup broke.

442
00:24:03,260 --> 00:24:04,220
But in my opinion,

443
00:24:04,740 --> 00:24:06,140
No matter who broke it,

444
00:24:06,380 --> 00:24:07,580
Huaiji is the one

445
00:24:08,100 --> 00:24:09,620
to be blamed for being disrespect the Emperor.

446
00:24:10,060 --> 00:24:11,740
He didn’t check the box

447
00:24:11,980 --> 00:24:12,740
while taking it.

448
00:24:12,980 --> 00:24:15,060
It indicates that he’s too careless to

449
00:24:15,580 --> 00:24:17,020
have it delivered

450
00:24:17,020 --> 00:24:18,300
as the emperor’s gift

451
00:24:18,460 --> 00:24:20,220
to the hand of the courtier.

452
00:24:20,660 --> 00:24:22,260
That means, he’s not in awe of

453
00:24:22,380 --> 00:24:23,300
Your Majesty’s intention.

454
00:24:24,060 --> 00:24:26,380
Awe is the essence of Rites.
Disrespect is disobeying rites.

455
00:24:27,180 --> 00:24:28,940
That’s a big deal
and he should be punished severely

456
00:24:29,340 --> 00:24:30,380
as the warning to the other.

457
00:24:32,980 --> 00:24:34,580
But he did it all out of kindness!

458
00:24:35,260 --> 00:24:36,180
The eunuch on duty was sick.

459
00:24:36,180 --> 00:24:37,980
If the delivery was delayed,

460
00:24:38,300 --> 00:24:40,140
he’d be punished.

461
00:24:40,700 --> 00:24:42,380
As a eunuch,

462
00:24:42,380 --> 00:24:44,740
Huaiji didn’t want his peer to be punished
out of this.

463
00:24:45,180 --> 00:24:46,500
He’s a nice gentleman

464
00:24:46,780 --> 00:24:48,980
who doesn’t want to see anyone suffering.

465
00:24:54,820 --> 00:24:55,780
Mr. Sima has a comment

466
00:24:56,820 --> 00:24:58,980
on this.

467
00:24:59,860 --> 00:25:01,660
Huaiji, serve the paper and ink.

468
00:25:10,700 --> 00:25:11,700
In a word,

469
00:25:13,660 --> 00:25:16,820
He loves me in deep heart.

470
00:25:18,220 --> 00:25:19,020
but

471
00:25:20,100 --> 00:25:21,900
he has to marry the other women.

472
00:25:23,100 --> 00:25:25,580
I cried and screamed

473
00:25:26,460 --> 00:25:30,340
even committed suicide.

474
00:25:32,700 --> 00:25:33,420
See?

475
00:25:37,940 --> 00:25:41,020
Aunt, you love Chief Xia so much.

476
00:25:45,580 --> 00:25:46,580
By now,

477
00:25:50,540 --> 00:25:53,740
I don’t know what love is.

478
00:25:54,900 --> 00:25:57,020
What I know is hate.

479
00:25:59,100 --> 00:26:00,340
I hate his wife.

480
00:26:02,300 --> 00:26:03,180
You surely will.

481
00:26:04,780 --> 00:26:07,660
Aunt, why didn’t you tell me this earlier?

482
00:26:08,060 --> 00:26:08,860
I would have…

483
00:26:08,860 --> 00:26:09,540
Bihan,

484
00:26:12,420 --> 00:26:13,340
I won’t bother you

485
00:26:13,340 --> 00:26:14,900
with my own business.

486
00:26:15,380 --> 00:26:16,660
I just want to help you.

487
00:26:17,580 --> 00:26:20,220
I’ll try my best to

488
00:26:20,540 --> 00:26:22,020
take good care of you.

489
00:26:22,500 --> 00:26:24,060
After you recover

490
00:26:24,580 --> 00:26:26,380
and give birth to a healthy prince,

491
00:26:27,020 --> 00:26:29,380
we shall put the other things into the agenda.

492
00:26:30,660 --> 00:26:31,540
Just relax.

493
00:26:32,940 --> 00:26:34,380
We need time to figure everything out.

494
00:26:37,420 --> 00:26:38,860
Don’t shake the jade glass while drinking.

495
00:26:39,380 --> 00:26:41,340
I used to hear this in a ceremony.

496
00:26:42,100 --> 00:26:43,500
Don’t wave the jade glass while drinking.

497
00:26:44,100 --> 00:26:46,580
This is from the Book of Rites.

498
00:26:47,420 --> 00:26:49,260
Wave means shake.

499
00:26:50,420 --> 00:26:52,020
Such casual behavior

500
00:26:52,260 --> 00:26:53,700
may cause the breaking of the jade glass.

501
00:26:55,140 --> 00:26:56,260
Then, why

502
00:26:56,620 --> 00:26:58,420
did they still use

503
00:26:58,980 --> 00:27:00,420
such a precious and fragile jade glass

504
00:27:00,500 --> 00:27:02,340
at the crowed ceremony?

505
00:27:04,140 --> 00:27:05,980
Only precious drinking vessel could

506
00:27:06,060 --> 00:27:07,300
show the high class manner.

507
00:27:12,820 --> 00:27:13,860
I thought the reason why

508
00:27:14,060 --> 00:27:16,380
people use this precious and fragile jade glass

509
00:27:16,380 --> 00:27:17,660
at the ceremony

510
00:27:18,220 --> 00:27:19,900
is to warn people to behave their selves .

511
00:27:20,620 --> 00:27:22,060
Using precious vessels

512
00:27:22,460 --> 00:27:24,180
could attract people’s attention to the rites

513
00:27:24,820 --> 00:27:26,300
and show their respect to each other.

514
00:27:26,860 --> 00:27:27,900
Courtier

515
00:27:28,220 --> 00:27:30,260
must be in awe of His Majesty.

516
00:27:30,980 --> 00:27:33,060
= Gao Taotao =
That’s why he should be careful and cautious

517
00:27:33,340 --> 00:27:35,140
to the emperor’s gift and his oral instructions.

518
00:27:35,980 --> 00:27:38,140
Eunuch Huaiji’s careless

519
00:27:38,660 --> 00:27:40,620
means he didn’t pay that much tribute
to Your Majesty.

520
00:27:41,420 --> 00:27:42,660
Within the imperial city,

521
00:27:43,140 --> 00:27:44,460
aren’t the lack of respect and rites

522
00:27:44,740 --> 00:27:46,380
the most severe transgressions to commit?

523
00:27:49,220 --> 00:27:50,940
Zongshi studies the Book of Rites well,

524
00:27:51,380 --> 00:27:52,580
and has a comprehensive understanding of this.

525
00:27:55,260 --> 00:27:57,580
I don’t like this Book of Rites.

526
00:27:57,660 --> 00:27:59,300
Brother Zongshi used to be an

527
00:27:59,300 --> 00:28:00,740
honest and simple gentleman.

528
00:28:00,860 --> 00:28:01,620
He makes such a long speech

529
00:28:02,060 --> 00:28:02,980
with these crap

530
00:28:02,980 --> 00:28:04,540
he learned from the book.

531
00:28:04,780 --> 00:28:06,180
What he means

532
00:28:06,180 --> 00:28:08,460
is to bully this accommodating eunuch.

533
00:28:08,780 --> 00:28:10,380
I’d rather not to read such

534
00:28:10,380 --> 00:28:11,460
a book which educates people
to be selfish and cold.

535
00:28:12,300 --> 00:28:13,300
Princess Fukang,

536
00:28:13,940 --> 00:28:15,740
Are you saying this out of control just
because His Majesty is here?

537
00:28:15,820 --> 00:28:18,380
Does this mean you can do anything you want
regardless of the etiquettes?

538
00:28:24,220 --> 00:28:27,380
Sorry for my impoliteness.
I can take punishment,

539
00:28:29,820 --> 00:28:31,340
even by kneeling,

540
00:28:31,340 --> 00:28:33,020
or beating palms.

541
00:28:33,700 --> 00:28:36,620
But it’s unfair to punish Huaiji.

542
00:28:37,420 --> 00:28:39,180
It’s not fair.

543
00:28:39,740 --> 00:28:41,460
Not fair at all.

544
00:28:41,900 --> 00:28:43,460
I am not convinced

545
00:28:44,180 --> 00:28:46,020
for ten thousand of reasons.

546
00:29:04,860 --> 00:29:05,860
Here’s the second sentence

547
00:29:06,460 --> 00:29:07,860
that Sima Guang said to me.

548
00:29:09,940 --> 00:29:11,180
Fancy stuff could always be fragile
and easy to disappear.

549
00:29:11,820 --> 00:29:14,140
Mistakes of the servant by accident
could also be forgiven.

550
00:29:17,020 --> 00:29:19,380
Fancy stuff like rosy cloud

551
00:29:19,900 --> 00:29:21,300
is easy to disappear.

552
00:29:21,900 --> 00:29:24,700
Making complaints
about the disappear of the fancy things

553
00:29:24,820 --> 00:29:25,900
makes no sense

554
00:29:26,540 --> 00:29:27,620
Now that the mistake has been made,

555
00:29:27,820 --> 00:29:30,060
why not let the man off the hook?

556
00:29:30,660 --> 00:29:33,380
Forgiveness is also a kind of kindness.

557
